&lt;h2 id="google-dorking"&gt;Google Dorking&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Google advanced search operators to surface hidden data.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;site:example.com # restrict to domain
filetype:pdf # specific file type
intitle:&amp;#34;index of&amp;#34; # directory listings
inurl:admin # URL contains string
&amp;#34;@gmail.com&amp;#34; site:pastebin.com # find leaked emails
cache:example.com # cached version of page
link:example.com # pages linking to site
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;Combine operators:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code&gt;site:linkedin.com intitle:&amp;#34;at CompanyName&amp;#34;
filetype:xls site:gov.uk password
inurl:&amp;#34;/wp-content/uploads/&amp;#34; filetype:pdf confidential
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id="email-header-analysis"&gt;Email Header Analysis&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email headers reveal routing, originating IP, mail client, and spam indicators.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Tools</title><link>https://rowstu.net/osint/tools/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://rowstu.net/osint/tools/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="osint-tools-reference"&gt;OSINT Tools Reference&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id="command-line-tools"&gt;Command-Line Tools&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="sherlock"&gt;Sherlock&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hunt down social media accounts by username across 300+ platforms.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Install&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pip install sherlock-project
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Basic usage&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sherlock username
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Output to file&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sherlock username --output results.txt
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Check specific sites&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sherlock username --site Twitter --site Instagram
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id="maigret"&gt;Maigret&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Username OSINT across 2000+ sites with detailed reports.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Install&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pip install maigret
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Run against username&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;maigret username
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Generate PDF report&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;maigret username --pdf
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# JSON output&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;maigret username --json report.json
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id="holehe"&gt;Holehe&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Check whether an email address is registered on 120+ websites.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>